title: Developers Testing More, JetBrains Study Finds
author: Loraine Lawson; Lawrence E Hecht
description: Also: Weaviate launches a hosted embedding service for AI apps, Tabnine checks licenses on AI-generated code, and Gemini Flash updates.
cntitle: 开发者测试更多，JetBrains 研究发现
cndescription: 此外：Weaviate 推出面向 AI 应用的托管嵌入服务，Tabnine 检查 AI 生成的代码许可证，以及 Gemini Flash 更新。
